#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:31
#, java-format
msgid "{0} extension is now available on all WikiMedia wikis."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:32
msgid "It identifies wikitext patterns that must or can be fixed in pages."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:33
msgid "It also provides some guidance about what the issues are with those patterns and how to fix them."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:35
msgid "You can help by fixing problems identified by the Linter extension."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:36
#, java-format
msgid "Integration between {0} and the Linter extension is done in the following way:"
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:38
msgid "The \"Linter categories\" button in this window lets you retrieve a list of pages detected by Linter for a given type of problem."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:39
msgid "The \"Check article with Linter\" button in the analysis window lets you check the current version of an article against Linter."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:40
#, java-format
msgid "Some errors detected by Linter are also reported directly by {0}."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:43
#, java-format
msgid "WPCleaner configuration is available online, check the {0}System configuration{1}."
msgstr "A configuración do WPCleaner está dispoñible en liña, revise o {0} configuración do Sistema {1}."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:46
msgid "Please, report any other problem you find to me."
msgstr "Por favor, avíseme de calquera problema que atope."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:49
#, java-format
msgid "I hope you''ll like {0}."
msgstr "Espero que lle guste {0}."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:50
#, java-format
msgid "I try to keep {0} up to date with Check Wiki, but if you find any discrepancy(ies) in the detections, please let me know."
msgstr "Tento manter {0} actualizado con Check Wiki, pero se atopa algunha discrepancia(s) nas deteccións, avíseme por favor."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:51
msgid "The Check Wiki project has evolved a lot recently."
msgstr "O proxecto Check Wiki evolucionou moito recentemente."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:52
msgid "New detections have been added either with new error numbers or by replacing previously used error numbers."
msgstr "Engadíronse novas deteccións con novos números de erro ou substituíndo números de erro usados anteriormente."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:53
msgid "You may need to update the Check Wiki translation file on your wiki to configure the new detections."
msgstr "Necesita actualizar o ficheiro de tradución de Check Wiki na súa wiki para configurar as novas deteccións."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:54
msgid "Disambiguator extension has been deployed to all WMF wikis."
msgstr "A extensión de Homónimos xa foi instalada en tódalas wikis WMF."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:55
msgid "It defines the new magic word __DISAMBIG__."
msgstr "Define a nova palabra máxica _DISAMBIG_."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:56
msgid "This magic word should be added to all disambiguation pages (either through templates or directly)."
msgstr "Esta palabra máxica debería ser engadida a tódalas páxinas de homónimos (a través de modelos ou directamente)."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:57
msgid "WPCleaner v1.28 also uses this as the default system."
msgstr ""

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:58
msgid "An action may be required on your wiki:"
msgstr "Pode que a súa wiki requira dunha acción:"

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:60
#, java-format
msgid "You can check if {0} is used on your wiki by opening an existing disambiguation page (like \"Smith\"). Then, click on \"Page information\" in the menu on the left. Finally, search for {0} in the information page."
msgstr "Pode comprobar se {0} se usa na súa wiki abrindo unha páxina de homónimos existente (como \"Santa Elena\", por exemplo). Logo, prema en \"Información da páxina\" no menú da esquerda. Por último, busque {0} na páxina de información."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:64
#, java-format
msgid "If {0} is not used on your wiki, you should add {1} to the page {2}."
msgstr "Se {0} non se usa na súa wiki, deberá engadir {1} á páxina {2}."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:70
msgid "Many new features were added recently : try them !"
msgstr "Engadíronse moitas características novas recentemente: próbeas!"

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:72
msgid "Leaving a note on talk pages with the list of links to disambiguation pages."
msgstr "Dixando unha nota nas páxinas de conversa cunha lista de ligazóns a páxinas de homónimos."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:73
msgid "Fixing errors detected by the Check Wiki project, in the full analysis window."
msgstr "Reparando erros detectados polo Wikiproxecto Check Wikipedia, na xanela de análise completo."

#: org/wikipediacleaner/Version.java:74
msgid "Fixing spelling or typography based on a list of suggestions."
msgstr "Amañando erros de escritura e ortográficos baseándose nunha lista de suxestións."

